(## 1. System Overview) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(This is a monorepo MVP implementing a B2C "save from X + chat over saved corpus" workflow with) Tj
0 -12 Td
(three runtime components:) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(1. `apps/api` \(FastAPI + Postgres + pgvector\)) Tj
0 -12 Td
(2. `apps/web` \(Next.js App Router + Clerk auth + dashboard\)) Tj
0 -12 Td
(3. `apps/extension` \(Chrome MV3 extension for capture + side panel chat\)) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(The architecture is intentionally simple:) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- Postgres is both system-of-record and vector store.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- Ingestion and embedding are synchronous during request handling.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- Extension authentication uses PAT.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- Web authentication uses Clerk; web server forwards Clerk identity headers to API.) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
